## PR Description
- Introduced an interface for Status message, and added two versions (phase0 and fulu); including schema definitions.
- Updated `StatusMessageFactory` with logic to return a `RpcRequestBodySelector` for both supported versions;
- Updated `StatusMessageHandler` to support decoding v1/v2 status messages;
- Updated `Peer`, `LibP2PPeer` and others with logic to send a request using `RpcRequestBodySelector` as a parameter;
- Updated existing methods to send a request without versioning to use `SingleRpcRequestBodySelector`;
- Updated all tests etc. 

## Fixed Issue(s)
related to #9539

